@TrendyApi_HostAddress = http://localhost:5261

### Health Check
GET {{TrendyApi_HostAddress}}/weatherforecast/
Accept: application/json

###

### Create Product with Images
POST {{TrendyApi_HostAddress}}/product
Content-Type: multipart/form-data

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="ShortDescriptionEn"

Premium Wireless Headphones
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="ShortDescriptionAr"

سماعة لاسلكية ممتازة
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="FullDescriptionEn"

High-quality wireless headphones with noise cancellation and 30-hour battery life. Perfect for music lovers and professionals.
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="FullDescriptionAr"

سماعة لاسلكية عالية الجودة مع إلغاء الضوضاء وعمر بطارية يصل إلى 30 ساعة. مثالية لعشاق الموسيقى والمحترفين.
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="Price"

299.99
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="Discount"

10.0
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="Quantity"

100
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="CategoryId"

1
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="StoreId"

1
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="Images"; filename="image1.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./test-image.jpg
--boundary--

###

### Get All Products
GET {{TrendyApi_HostAddress}}/product
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Product by ID
GET {{TrendyApi_HostAddress}}/product/1
Accept: application/json

###

### Update Product
PUT {{TrendyApi_HostAddress}}/product/1
Content-Type: multipart/form-data

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="ShortDescriptionEn"

Updated Premium Headphones
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="ShortDescriptionAr"

سماعة محدثة
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="FullDescriptionEn"

Updated description
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="FullDescriptionAr"

وصف محدث
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="Price"

349.99
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="Discount"

15.0
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="Quantity"

50
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="CategoryId"

1
--boundary

###

### Delete Product
DELETE {{TrendyApi_HostAddress}}/product/1
Accept: application/json

###
